markets.title: Will Trump win the Electoral College and Trump win the Popular Vote?
markets.yes_sub_title: Trump wins Electoral College, Trump wins Popular Vote
markets.no_sub_title: Trump wins Electoral College, Trump wins Popular Vote
markets.expiration_value: Trump wins Electoral College, Trump wins Popular Vote
markets.rules_primary: If the Republican Party wins the Electoral College and the Republican Party wins the Popular Vote for the U.S. Presidency in  2024, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: The market turns specifically on the party of the person who wins either the Popular Vote or Electoral College. So if the candidates are replaced by members of the same party, the market will still resolve based on whether a member of that party wins the Popular Vote and/or Electoral College.
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close following the release of the Underlying data.
